			+ '<li><p>Opt&#45;out of Online Behavioral Advertising provided by AT&#38;T and other advertisers on your computer by clicking the &#34;<a href="http://www.att.com/internal/adchoices" target="_blank">Advertising Choices</a>" &#34; link at the bottom of our web pages&#46;</p></li>'
			+ '<li><p>Opt&#45;out of Relevant Advertising by AT&#38;T on Satellite TV Viewing <a href="/cmpchoice" title="Opt&#45;out of Relevant Advertising by AT&#38;T on Satellite TV Viewing" target="_blank">here</a>&#46;</a></p></li>'
			+ '<li><p>Opt-out of interest-based advertising on att.net powered by Yahoo! <a href="http://info.yahoo.com/privacy/us/yahoo/opt_out/targeting/details.html" title="Yahoo! Interest-Based Advertising Opt Out" target="_blank">here</a>.</p></li>'
			+ '<li><p>Opt-out of online behavioral advertising from many other ad networks <a href="http://www.networkadvertising.org/choices/" title="Network Advertising Choices" target="_blank">at the Network Advertising Initiative (NAI) site</a>..</p></li>'
