			+ '<p>For assistance in other languages, please visit <a href="http://world.att.com" target="_blank" title="AT&amp;T World">world.att.com</a>.</p>'
			+ '<p>Legacy AT&amp;T Consumer - 1-800-222-0300</p>'

			+ '<p>Restricting our use of your CPNI for marketing purposes will not affect the provision of any AT&amp;T products or services to which you subscribe, nor will it eliminate all types of AT&amp;T marketing contacts.</p>'
			+'<h3 class="accent1" style="margin-top:30px;" id="att-contact">Customer Service Contact Numbers</h3>'
			 + '<p><strong>Wireless</strong> &#8212; 1-800-331-0500</p>'
